description:
Unwanted Edition Digital Sad Bunny NFTs.

For the last time ever, collect your own ridiculous digital non-collectible NFT. Each NFT is not a collectible, it automatically entitles one to experience a transaction. Add to your NFT collection just for fun. A great way to test a new wallet address be it desktop or mobile. Impress your friends with this Sad Bunny NFT. Art work has a clear background.
name: Take the Bunny and Run
